ssassination%20attempt%20on%20former%20President%20Trump%20on%20July%2013.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnalysts%20now%20expect%20more%20market%20volatility%20after%20Biden%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20race.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-dropping-out-presidential-race-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20presidential%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20throwing%20fresh%20uncertainty%20into%20the%20markets%20for%20a%20second%20straight%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20were%20already%20trying%20to%20position%20themselves%20for%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftrump-trade-dominate-markets-weekend-shooting-bitcoin-dollar-inflation-bonds-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20trade%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20failed%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20July%2013.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20Biden%20dropping%20out%20would%20change%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20are%20gearing%20up%20for%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20some%20rotation%20toward%20'red'%20sectors%20and%20away%20from%20'blue'%20ones%20in%20recent%20weeks%20as%20recent%20momentum%20has%20favored%20the%20Republican%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Haefele%2C%20UBS%20Global%20Wealth%20Management's%20chief%20investment%20officer%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BThat%20could%20at%20least%20partially%20reverse%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20as%20markets%20parse%20the%20latest%20developments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20dollar%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20gain%20under%20a%20potential%20Trump%20presidency%20%E2%80%94%20weakened%20on%20Monday.%20This%20helped%20dollar-denominated%20spot%20gold%20rise%200.2%25%20to%20above%20%242%2C400%20an%20ounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20at%20large%20were%20relatively%20calm%20following%20Biden's%20withdrawal%20after%20the%20Trump%20trade%20gripped%20sentiment%20last%20week.%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stock%20futures%20were%200.2%25%20at%201%3A33%20a.m.%20ET%2C%20while%20Nasdaq-100%20futures%20were%20up%200.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYields%20for%2010-year%20US%20Treasury%20yields%20were%201.7%20basis%20points%20lower%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20may%20reflect%20a%20little%20less%20risk%20of%20even%20more%20fiscal%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20Jim%20Reid%2C%20a%20multi-asset%20research%20strategist%20at%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20EUROSTOXX%2050%20and%20FTSE%20futures%20were%20slightly%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyle%20Rodda%2C%20a%20senior%20market%20analyst%20at%20trading%20platform%20Capital.com%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Biden's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20race%20also%20removes%20a%20layer%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20move%20probably%20improves%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20Democrats%20to%20win%20the%20presidency%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodda%2C%20referring%20to%20Biden's%20decision%20not%20to%20seek%20a%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%2C%20as%20a%20safe%20haven%20asset%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20under%20pressure%20should%20Harris'%20chances%20improve%2C%20since%20it%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20fallout%20from%20Trump's%20hawkish%20foreign%20policy%20and%20massive%20deficit%20spending%2C%20Chris%20Weston%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20at%20Australian%20onine%20broker%20Pepperstone%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3f48522-54de-4da9-82d3-437e495c1682%5C%22%3EInvestors%20are%20watching%20to%20see%20if%20Harris%20wins%20the%20Democrats'%20nomination%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20still%20focusing%20on%20whether%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20will%20nominate%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20its%20presidential%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20small%20risk%20that%20Harris'%20presumptive%20nomination%20is%20met%20with%20resistance%20within%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20causes%20internal%20divisions%2C%20leading%20to%20calls%20for%20another%20candidate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodda.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20reignite%20the%20volatility%20we%20saw%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBOE%20Volatility%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E%20rose%2033%25%20last%20week%20following%20the%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Trump%2C%20reflecting%20market%20jitters%20over%20the%20political%20landscape.%20The%20index%20was%20not%20yet%20open%20for%20trade%20on%20Monday%20as%20of%20the%20time%20this%20article%20was%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20don't%20expect%20the%20Democrats'%20fiscal%20and%20trade%20policy%20agenda%20to%20shift%20much%20if%20they%20nominate%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Dems%20will%20want%20to%20position%20her%20as%20a%20continuity%20candidate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiden's%20withdrawal%20resets%20the%20contest.%20However%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20Harris%20is%20nominated%20to%20succeed%20Biden%20as%20the%20Democratic%20standard-bearer%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20election%20will%20not%20change%20as%20much%20as%20one%20might%20expect%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20UBS'%20Haefele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20electorate%20is%20highly%20polarized%20and%20most%20of%20Biden's%20supporters%20will%20be%20reluctant%20to%20abandon%20the%20party's%20nominee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e61103fa-8cc5-45d1-b7c4-8f13267a9b79%5C%22%3EFocus%20on%20fundamentals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20uncertainty%2C%20UBS%20advises%20investors%20to%20not%20forget%20fundamentals%20matter%20too%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20even%20more%20so%20than%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20should%20r