Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20not%20raised%20by%20BJP%20ally%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20reported%20Congress's%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20BJP%20ally%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20minister%20and%20chief%20of%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20spoke%20of%20the%20controversial%20eateries%20order.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20that%20the%20order%20was%20taken%20without%20much%20thought%20and%20the%20government%20is%20adamant%20on%20it%20because%20the%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20all-party%20meet%2C%20Union%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20asked%20the%20Opposition%20to%20avoid%20disruptions%20during%20the%20speeches%20of%20senior%20leaders.%20During%20parliament's%20inaugural%20session%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20reply%20to%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20on%20the%20President's%20address%2C%20was%20repeatedly%20interrupted%20by%20slogan-shouting%20by%20the%20Opposition%20members.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20budget%20session%20will%20conclude%20on%20August%2012%2C%20by%20which%20time%2C%20the%20government%20aims%20to%20pass%20six%20bills%20including%20one%20which%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%2090-year-old%20Aircraft%20Act%20to%20enhance%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20in%20the%20aviation%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721626560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9mga7t98_lok-sabha-generic-ani-_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-braces-for-opposition-storm-as-budget-session-begins-today-10-points-6156879%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parliament's%20budget%20session%20will%20begin%20today%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20multiple%20controversies%20including%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20NEET%20and%20Manipur.%20Three%20states%2C%20two%20of%20them%20ruled%20by%20allies%2C%20are%20demanding%20special%20status.%20The%20Union