fter%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%202024%20race%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bhonored%20to%20have%20the%20President's%20endorsement%20and%20my%20intention%20is%20to%20earn%20and%20win%20this%20nomination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Ms%20Harris'%20entry%20in%20the%20US%20Presidential%20elections%2C%20the%20speculation%20about%20who%20could%20be%20her%20Vice%20President%20pick%20has%20begun.%20Among%20the%20names%20doing%20the%20rounds%20is%20Arizona%20Senator%20Mark%20Kelly.%20Within%20minutes%20of%20Harris'%20post%2C%20Senator%20Kelly%20put%20out%20a%20message%20on%20the%20microblogging%20site%20X%20sharing%20his%20support%20for%20her.%20%26quot%3BKamala%20Harris%20is%20the%20right%20person%20to%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20lead%20the%20country%20into%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Kelly%20was%20elected%20in%20December%202020%20as%20a%20senator%20from%20Arizonan%20to%20fill%20out%20the%20remainder%20of%20John%20McCain's%20term.%20A%20navy%20veteran%2C%20who%20served%20as%20a%20combat%20pilot%20in%20Operation%20Desert%20Storm%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Kuwait%2C%20the%20lawmaker%20is%20also%20a%20former%20NASA%20astronaut.%20His%20first%20space%20mission%20was%20in%202001%20aboard%20Space%20Shuttle%20Endeavour%20and%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20he%20commanded%20the%20Space%20Shuttle's%20final%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Kelly%20has%20taken%20on%20the%20Republicans%20over%20issues%20like%20abortion%20and%20said%20Trump%20and%20his%20running%20mate%20JD%20Vance%20need%20to%20be%20kept%20out%20of%20office%20to%20restore%20abortion%20rights.%20In%20October%20last%20year%2C%20he%20travelled%20to%20Tel%20Aviv%20with%20a%20group%20of%20Senators%20and%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20pledged%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20possible%20running%20mate%20for%20Ms%20Harris%2C%20North%20Carolina%20Governor%20Roy%20Cooper%20has%20also%20backed%20her%20nomination.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20lead%20our%20country%20thoughtfully%20and%20with%20integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20background%20in%20law%2C%20he%20took%20over%20as%20Attorney%20General%20in%202000.%20He%20was%20elected%20Governor%20in%202016%20and%20re-elected%20in%202020.%20Governor%20Cooper%20has%20worked%20to%20combat%20the%20opioid%20crisis%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%20is%20credited%20with%20launching%20the%20state's%20first%20Opioid%20Action%20Plan%20in%202017.%20He%20also%20helped%20formulate%20Carolina's%20first%20children's%20health%20insurance%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPennsylvania%20Governor%20Josh%20Shapiro%20also%20endorsed%20Harris%20even%20as%20his%20name%20cropped%20up%20as%20a%20possible%20Vice%20Presidential%20candidate.%20Governor%20Shapiro%20said%20he%20will%20do%20everything%20he%20can%20to%20help%20elect%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20As%20the%20Governor%20of%20the%20state%20where%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20shot%20at%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20Governor%20Shapiro%20condemned%20the%20attack%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BViolence%20targeted%20at%20any%20political%20party%20or%20political%20leader%20is%20absolutely%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Shapiro%20assumed%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Governor%20of%20Pennsylvania%20last%20year%20in%20January.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20%C2%A0was%20elected%20as%20Pennsylvania's%20Attorney%20General.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20the%20Republicans%20alleged%20the%20election%20was%20rigged%2C%20he%20defended%20Pennsylvania's%20election%20result%2C%20winning%20in%20court%20dozens%20of%20times%20before%20and%20after%20Election%20Day.%20During%20his%20tenure%20as%20Attorney%20General%2C%20he%20exposed%20the%20Catholic%20Church