nder%20last%20week%20lost%20control%20of%20the%20company%20as%20a%20tribunal%20kick-started%20an%20insolvency%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccused%20of%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20mismanagement%20and%20compliance%20issues%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20family%20of%20teachers%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20south%20India%20faces%20a%20reckoning%20that%20will%20test%20the%20ingenuity%20that%20made%20him%20a%20poster%20child%20for%20India's%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20formerly%20high-flying%20company%20was%20eventually%20brought%20low%20when%20it%20could%20not%20pay%20%2419%20million%20in%20sponsorship%20dues%20to%20India's%20cricket%20federation%2C%20prompting%20a%20tribunal%20to%20suspend%20Byju's%20board%20and%20make%20Raveendran%20report%20to%20a%20court-appointed%20restructuring%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20appeals%20tribunal%20is%20expected%20to%20hold%20a%20hearing%20on%20Monday%20on%20whether%20Byju's%20insolvency%20process%20should%20be%20quashed%20after%20the%20former%20billionaire%20argued%20in%20court%20his%20company%20is%20solvent%20and%20that%20insolvency%20could%20shut%20it%20down%20and%20cost%20the%20jobs%20of%2027%2C000%20staff%2C%20including%20teachers.%20Insolvency%20also%20would%20not%20bode%20well%20for%20Byju's%20backers%2C%20such%20as%20Dutch%20technology%20investor%20Prosus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20denies%20the%20allegations%20of%20mismanagement%20and%20wrongdoing%20at%20his%20firm%2C%20which%20has%20in%20recent%20months%20faced%20lawsuits%20over%20unpaid%20loans%20and%20boardroom%20battles%20with%20foreign%20investors%20that%20went%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPotential%20insolvency%20is%20a%20dramatic%20turn%20of%20events%20for%20an%20entrepreneur%20described%20by%20one%20person%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20him%20as%20an%20extremely%20passionate%20and%20goal-oriented%20person%20who%20might%20adopt%20%26quot%3Ban%20abrasive%20approach%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20presented%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuave%2C%20nice%20and%20polished%26quot%3B%20image%2C%20appearing%20to%20heed%20the%20advice%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Beventually%20there%20was%20a%20trust%20deficit%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20another%20executive%20who%20quit%20last%20year%20as%20Byju's%20senior%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%20things%20are%20improving%2C%20don't%20worry%2C%20we%20have%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20executive%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20and%20Byju's%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBYJU'S%20DOWNFALL%3A%20'OUR%20FAIR%20SHARE%20OF%20MISTAKES'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20engineer%20by%20training%2C%20he%20started%20Byju's%20in%202011%20with%20physical%20classes%20after%20friends%20urged%20him%20to%20go%20into%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%2C%20who%20aced%20his%20management%20exam%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20score%20of%20100%20percentile%2C%20not%20once%20but%20twice%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company%20website%2C%20started%20what%20would%20become%20his%20empire%20with%20his%20wife%20Divya%20Gokulnath%2C%2038%2C%20a%20former%20student%20of%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20education-obsessed%20country%2C%20Raveendran%20hit%20gold%20by%20offering%20online%20teaching%20programs%20priced%20from%20%24100%20to%20%24300.%20He%20got%20a%20mammoth%20boost%20when%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20sent%20students%20indoors.%20At%20the%20height%20of%20his%20fame%20in%202021%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%244%20billion%2C%20Forbes%20reckoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20all%20that%20is%20in%20tatters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20reversal%20of%20Byju's%20meteoric%20success%2C%20say%20executives%20and%20advisers%20who%20worked%20with%20Raveendran%2C%20is%20that%20he%20overruled%20associates%20and%20expanded%20the%20business%20through%20expensive%20acquisitions%2C%20splurging%20on%20marketing%20and%20being%20slow%20to%20address%20problems%20such%20as%20sales%20agents%20adopting%20aggressive%20tactics%20to%20mis-sell%20courses%20that%20damaged%20the%20company's%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20backing%20of%20investors%20like%20General%20Atlantic%2C%20Prosus%20and%20Facebook%20founder%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20philanthropy%20venture%2C%20Raveendran%20spent%20millions%20on%20acquisitions%2C%20and%20the%20company%20says%20it%20has%20150%20million%20students%20in%20over%20100%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20growing%20fast%2C%20as%20I've%20accepted%20multiple%20times%2C%20we've%20made%20our%20fair%20share%20of%20mistakes%26quot%3B%2C%20Raveendran%20told%20an%20interviewer%20last%20year%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20battled%20crises%2C%20the%20CEO%20also%20said%20decisions%20to%20lay%20off%20some%20of%20its%20then-50%2C000%20employees%20and%20slash%20branding%20expenses%20would%20help%20strengthen%20loss-making%20Byju's%20and%20turn%20its%20cashflow%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20country%20needs%20a%20Byju's%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721617680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fagghgamg_byju-raveendran_625x300_22_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-founder-faces-reckoning-as-companys-valuation-drops-to-2-billion-6158443%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Byju%20Raveendran%2C%20the%20mathematics%20whiz%20who%20soared%20from%20teacher%20to%20startup%20billionaire%20before%20his%20education%20technology%20company%20imploded%20this%20year%2C%20now%20faces%20his%20biggest%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyjus-fo