-conference-3-big-questions-india-head-coach-needs-to-answer-6158343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-press-conference-3-big-questions-india-head-coach-needs-to-answer-6158343%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-press-conference-3-big-questions-india-head-coach-needs-to-answer-6158343%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20A%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Will%20Need%20Viksit%2C%20Intelligent%20Villages%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fsites%2F3%2F2019%2F12%2F30173704%2Fmanipur_cleanest_village_istock_660x330.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESwadesh%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20released%20in%202004%2C%20was%20a%20landmark%20movie%20in%20which%20the%20young%20hero%2C%20Mohan%20Bhargav%2C%20portrayed%20rather%20brilliantly%20by%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20goes%20back%2C%20straight%20from%20building%20rockets%20at%20NASA%2C%20to%20his%20village.%20The%20movie%20has%20a%20happy%20ending%2C%20with%20villagers%20building%20their%20own%20technology%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20hero.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20things%20aren't%20so%20good%20in%20the%20around%206%2C50%2C000%20villages%20housing%2065%25%20of%20India's%20population%2C%20that%20is%2C%20close%20to%2090%20crore%20people.%20These%20villages%20are%20largely%20driven%20by%20an%20agricultural%20economy.%20Trapped%20between%20increasing%20extreme%20climatic%20events%20like%20floods%20and%20drought%20and%20poor%20availability%20of%20affordable%20farm%20credit%2C%20they%20have%20a%20restless%20young%20population%20that%20aspires%20to%20migrate%20to%20cities%2C%20looking%20for%20ever-illusive%20jobs%20and%20their%20future%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERebuilding%20the%20decaying%20rural%20economy%20is%20going%20to%20get%20even%20tougher%20with%20the%20upcoming%20intelligence%20explosion%20and%20advances%20in%20AI%20%26amp%3B%20Robotics.%20These%20breakthroughs%20are%20threatening%20to%20upend%20how%20we%20live%2C%20work%20and%20travel%2C%20thus%20potentially%20driving%20up%20massive%20inequality%2C%20between%20the%20intelligence%20haves%20and%20have-nots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Intelligence%20Economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202030%2C%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%207.5%20billion%20connected%20humans%20will%20be%20living%20together%20with%2030%20billion%20intelligent%20and%20connected%20machines%20in%20the%20intelligence%20economy%2C%20creating%20%2415.7%20trillion%20of%20new%20economic%20value%20by%202030%2C%20according%20to%20PWC's%20research.%20The%20pace%20at%20which%20this%20change%20is%20occurring%20is%20unsettling%20even%20for%20a%20person%20like%20me%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20last%2015%20years%20working%20closely%20with%20AI%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20as%20an%20investor.%20Roughly%20speaking%2C%20we%20had%20taken%20300-plus%20years%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20world%20wars%20to%20absorb%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%2C%20and%20another%2050%20years%20to%20digest%20the%20IT%2FDigital%20revolution.%20But%20we%20are%20going%20to%20zip%20through%20the%20intelligence%20revolution%20in%20a%2010-15%20year%20time%20period.%20This%20transition%20is%20going%20to%20be%20rapid%20and%20might%20result%20in%20societal%20and%20geopolitical%20instability%2C%20unless%20planned%20carefully.%20If%20we%20try%20building%20Viksit%20Bharat%20without%20enabling%20our%20villages%20to%20leapfrog%20from%20a%20largely%20agriculture-based%20economy%20to%20the%20intelligence%20economy%2C%20we%20will%20soon%20see%20an%20abundance%20of%20humongous%20cities%20like%20Delhi%20that%20are%20hard%20to%20keep%20under%20control%20with%20their%20teeming%20migrant%20populations%2C%20eventually%20placing%20extreme%20pressure%20on%20the%20fragile%20environment.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20way%20forward%20is%20to%20surf%20the%20waves%20of%20change%20and%20opportunities%20that%20the%20intelligence%20economy%20is%20bringing%20to%20the%20table%20and%20leverage%20it%20to%20build%20a%20digital-physical%20twin%20of%20the%20sustainable%20developmental%20model%20for%20a%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Village%26quot%3B%2C%20embodying%20these%20seven%20strategic%20pillars%20of%20technological%20innovations-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvanced%20infrastructure%20housing%20intelligent%205G%2F6G-connected%20utilities%20that%20manage%20grid-level%20air%2C%20water%2C%20waste%20and%20mobility.%20This%20would%20be%20powered%20by%20renewable%20energy%20sources%2C%20solar%20and%20waste%20to%20energy%20systems.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENext-generational%20agriculture%20with%20precision%20farming%20and%20automated%20agribots%20connected%20to%20autonomous%20supply%20chains%20globally.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrecision%20manufacturing%20pods%20with%20localised%20micro-manufacturing%20driven%20by%20versatile%20robots.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPersonalised%20intelligent%20healthcare%20and%20education%20that%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20AI%20age%20with%20XR%20devices%20and%20AI%20co-explorers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIntelligence-driven%20local%20industries%20paired%20with%20remote%20digital%20work%20for%20data%20annotations%20and%20monitoring%20service%20bots.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDigital%20public%20intelligence-driven%20local%20self-governance%2C%20with%20AI%20courts%20for%20rapid%20justice%20at%20district%20level.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20growth%20of%20sustainable%20development%2C%20which%20a%20man-machine%20society%20with%20environmental%2C%20social%2C%20mental%20and%20spiritual%20aspects%20needs%20to%20grow%20and%20prosper.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20this%20massive%20undertaking%20is%20clear%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20this%20technological%20change%20and%20modelling%20its%20impact%20on%20society%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20task.%20Globally%20speaking%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20couple%20attempts%20at%20building%20technologically-driven%20and%20advanced%20cities%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Masdar%20City%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20Songdo%20in%20South%20Korea.%20But%20very%20few%20have%20actually%20attempted%20to%20construct%20a%20live%20site%20at%20this%20scale%20to%20model%20the%20changes%20needed%20for%20our%20developing%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Moonshot%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20adopt%20the%20moonshot%20approach%2C%20taking%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20the%20late%20JFK's%20vision%20to%20reach%20the%20moon%2C%20as%20we%20have%20seen%20how%20this%20built%20the%20industrial%20economy%20and%20the%20military%20complex%20of%20the%20USA.%20Considering%20the%20ready%20availability%20of%20land%20needed%20to%20build%20a%20place%20as%20impactful%20as%20this%2C%20Bengaluru%20(where%20the%20talent%20and%20capital%20required%20for%20research%20and%20development%20of%20such%20a%20complex%20ecosystem%20is%20readily%20available)%20comes%20to%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20initial%20take-off%2C%20we%20can%20look%20at%20existing%20PSUs%20(Public%20Sector%20Units)%20that%20are%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20futuristic%20technology%20infusion%20to%20survive%20and%20create%20a%20symbiotic%20relationship%20with%20an%20aim%20towards%20economic%20rebirth.%20An%20existing%20example%20is%20the%20HMT%20campus%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20was%20initially%20set%20up%20to%20bring%20in%20precision%20manufacturing%20innovations%20in%20the%20early%201950s.%20It%20was%20the%20dream%20organisation%20for%20many%20while%20being%20the%20embodiment%20of%20manufacturing%20excellence.%20HMT%20also%20holds%20a%20place%20in%20my%20heart%20as%20my%20father%20bought%20me%20my%20very%20first%20watch%20from%20HMT.%20Changes%20in%20the%20technological%20landscape%20mean%20that%20the%20HMT%20needs%20a%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20re-innovation%26quot%3B%20of%20purpose%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHMT%20As%20A%20Launchpad%20-%20An%20Example%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PSU's%20unused%20land%20and%20resources%20can%20be%20used%20in%20a%20public-private%20model%20to%20create%20the%20site%20for%20the%20intelligent%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Village%20''%20that%20is%20built%20around%20the%20seven%20key%20strategic%20technological%20pillars%20outlined%20above.%20Envisioned%20on%20a%20400-acre%20campus%20that%20will%20be%20capable%20of%20housing%2010%2C000%20people%2C%20and%20built%20to%20vision%20the%20next%20generation%20embodying%20a%20sustainable%20future%2C%20it%20will%20feature%20innovation%20zones%20for%20AI%20and%20robotics%20startups%2C%20a%20global%20research%20institute%20for%20AI%20and%20robotics%2C%20global%20outsourcing%20hubs%20for%20data%20annotations%2C%20AI%20compute%20clusters%2C%20a%20data%20foundry%20and%20upskilling%20zones%20for%20existing%20employees%20and%20the%20workforce%20of%20HMT%20and%20other%20manufacturing%20giants%2C%20all%20working%20together%20to%20make%20the%20digital-physical%20twin%20real%2C%20may%20be%20at%20a%20pilot%20hub%20in%20the%20nearby%20Mandya%20district.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20viable%20economic%20model%20around%20land%20reuse%20for%20technological%20rebirth%20can%20mean%20that%20HMT's%20land%20will%20be%20a%20cradle%20for%20future%20technology%20innovations%20and%20a%20potential%20source%20of%20new%20technological%20IP.%20It%20can%20also%20act%20as%20a%20channel%20for%20a%20potential%20go-to%20market.%20Headed%20by%20an%20eminent%20advisory%20board%2C%20with%20industry%20leaders%20of%20repute%20and%20academia%2C%20ably%20supported%20by%20the%20government%20with%20a%20sizable%20initial%20grant%2C%20it%20can%20collaborate%20with%20leading%20Indian%20and%20global%20universities%20for%20long-term%20research%20under%20the%20newly%20formed%20NRF%20(National%20Research%20Foundation).%20It%20can%20also%20host%20global%20grand%20challenges%20for%20key%20technology%20and%20research%20problems%2C%20with%20built-in%20test%20beds%20for%20AI%20and%20robotics%20solutions%20in%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20autonomous%20mobility%20and%20agriculture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EScaling%20Up%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransforming%20both%20the%20ailing%20PSU%20and%20dormant%20villages%20with%20technology%20innovations%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Village%26quot%3B%20will%20make%20the%20vision%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20real.%20Once%20the%20developmental%20model%20is%20working%20on%20the%20pilot%20site%2C%20we%20can%20look%20at%20deploying%20and%20transforming%20initially%20100%20villages%20with%20these%20innovations.%20Post%20that%2C%20we%20can%20scale%20the%20model%20from%20the%20initial%20100%20to%20the%20whole%20of%20India's%206%2C50%2C000-plus%20villages%20eventually%2C%20while%20tweaking%20for%20impact%20and%20policy%20feedback.%20This%20bottom-up%20way%20of%20building%20the%20change%20that%20Viksit%20Bharat%20aims%20for%20might%20be%20more%20effective%20and%20less%20prone%20to%20failures%20than%20typical%20top-down%20execution%20via%20mere%20incentives%20and%20policy%20levers.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20technological%20innovation%20goldmine%20from%20this%20exhilarating%20and%20challenging%20journey%20will%20make%20the%20country%20the%20source%20of%20the%20advanced%20technologies%20needed%20for%20a%20sustainable%20tomorrow%20not%20just%20for%20India%20but%20also%20for%20the%20world.%20This%20may%20eventually%20make%20for%20a%20good%20plot%20for%20the%20sequel%20to%20the%20original%20movie%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3ESwadesh%202.0%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20the%20hero%20takes%20the%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Village%26quot%3B%20technologies%20from%20India%20back%20to%20the%20USA%20to%20make%20it%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20again%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20sustainable%20way.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Umakant%20Soni%20is%20chairman%20of%20AIfoundry%20and%20co-founder%20of%20ARTPARK(AI%20%26amp%3B%20Robotics%20Technology%20Park)%20%26amp%3B%20a%20passionate%20advocate%20for%20inclusive%20development)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721614920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fsites%2F3%2F2019%2F12%2F30173704%2Fmanipur_cleanest_village_istock_660x330.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-viksit-bharat-will-need-viksit-villages-too-6158340%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Transforming%20both%20the%20ailing%20PSU%20and%20dormant%20villages%20with%20technology%20innovations%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Village%26quot%3B%20will%20make%20the%20vision%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20real.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-viksit-bharat-will-need-viksit-villages-too-6158340%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-viksit-bharat-will-need-viksit-villages-too-6158340%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-viksit-bharat-will-need-viksit-villages-too-6158340%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20Alicent%20Hightower%20on%20'House%20of%20the%20Dragon%2C'%20if%20it%20follows%20her%20fate%20in%20the%20book%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red-haired%20woman%20in%20a%20green%20dress%20and%20black%20veil%20looking%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669a508580d4d5da13d54b68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOliv