20have%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20endorsement%20as%20the%20nominee%20of%20the%20Democratic%20party%20for%20the%20presidential%20election%20and%20asserted%20that%20her%20aim%20was%20to%20unite%20the%20nation%20in%20%26quot%3Bdefeating%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20extreme%20Project%202025%20agenda%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20remarks%20came%20after%20Biden%20(81)%2C%20in%20a%20stunning%20decision%2C%20on%20Sunday%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20race%20to%20be%20the%20next%20president%20in%202024%20and%20endorsed%20Harris%2C%20who%20is%20of%20both%20Indian%20and%20African%20origin%2C%20as%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20new%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20decision%20to%20nominate%20Harris%20(59)%20follows%20weeks%20of%20intense%20pressure%20from%20fellow%20Democrats%20after%20his%20disastrous%20presidential%20debate%20performance%20against%20his%20Republican%20rival%20and%20former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20honoured%20to%20have%20the%20President's%20endorsement%20and%20my%20intention%20is%20to%20earn%20and%20win%20this%20nomination%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harris%2C%20who%20has%20been%20serving%20as%20US'%20first%20female%2C%20first%20Black%20and%20first%20South%20Asian%20vice%20president%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Biden's%20endorsement%20almost%20seals%20her%20position%20as%20the%20presidential%20nominee%20of%20her%20party%2C%20she%20still%20needs%20to%20get%20elected%20by%20the%20party's%20delegates%20during%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20in%20Chicago%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20immediately%20secured%20the%20endorsement%20of%20former%20president%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20a%20bit%20easier%20for%20her%20to%20win%20the%20delegate%20battle%20during%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20in%20Chicago%20beginning%20August%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20American%20people%2C%20I%20thank%20Joe%20Biden%20for%20his%20extraordinary%20leadership%20as%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20for%20his%20decades%20of%20service%20to%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20said%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20she%20has%20travelled%20across%20the%20country%2C%20talking%20to%20Americans%20about%20the%20clear%20choice%20in%20this%20momentous%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20what%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20in%20the%20days%20and%20weeks%20ahead.%20I%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20my%20power%20to%20unite%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20--%20and%20unite%20our%20nation--%20to%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20extreme%20Project%202025%20agenda...%20We%20have%20107%20days%20until%20Election%20Day.%20Together%2C%20we%20will%20fight.%20And%20together%2C%20we%20will%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Hillary%20Clinton%20quickly%20endorsed%20Harris%20to%20be%20the%20nominee.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20lived%20through%20many%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20but%20nothing%20has%20made%20us%20more%20worried%20for%20our%20country%20than%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20a%20second%20Trump%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20promised%20to%20be%20a%20dictator%20on%20day%20one%2C%20and%20the%20recent%20ruling%20by%20his%20servile%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20only%20embolden%20him%20to%20further%20shred%20the%20Constitution.%20Now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20support%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20fight%20with%20everything%20we've%20got%20to%20elect%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Clintons%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20statement%2C%20Harris%20thanked%20Biden%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20country's%20people%20for%20his%20extraordinary%20leadership%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20remarkable%20legacy%20of%20accomplishment%20is%20unmatched%20in%20modern%20American%20history%2C%20surpassing%20the%20legacy%20of%20many%20Presidents%20who%20have%20served%20two%20terms%20in%20office.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20profound%20honour%20to%20serve%20as%20his%20vice%20president%2C%20and%20I%20am%20deeply%20grateful%20to%20the%20President%2C%20Dr%20Biden%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20Biden%20family.%20I%20first%20came%20to%20know%20President%20Biden%20through%20his%20son%20Beau.%20We%20were%20friends%20from%20our%20days%20working%20together%20as%20Attorneys%20General%20of%20our%20home%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20worked%20together%2C%20Beau%20would%20tell%20me%20stories%20about%20his%20dad.%20The%20kind%20of%20father%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20man%20he%20is.%20And%20the%20qualities%20Beau%20revered%20in%20his%20father%20are%20the%20same%20qualities%2C%20the%20same%20values%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20every%20single%20day%20in%20Joe's%20leadership%20as%20President%3A%20His%20honesty%20and%20integrity.%20His%20big%20heart%20and%20commitment%20to%20his%20faith%20and%20his%20family.%20And%20his%20love%20of%20our%20country%20and%20the%20American%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20selfless%20and%20patriotic%20act%2C%20President%20Biden%20is%20doing%20what%20he%20has%20done%20throughout%20his%20life%20of%20service%3A%20putting%20the%20American%20people%20and%20the%20country%20above%20everything%20else%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Biden%20announced%20that%20he%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20fellow%20Democrats%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20accept%20the%20nomination%20and%20to%20focus%20all%20my%20energies%20on%20my%20duties%20as%20President%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20my%20term.%20My%20very%20first%20decision%20as%20the%20party%20nominee%20in%202020%20was%20to%20pick%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20my%20Vice%20President.%20And%20it's%20been%20the%20best%20d