0They%20are%20the%20future%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Biden%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%20beat%20Trump%2C%20though%20the%20Republican%20never%20accepted%20his%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20his%20main%20mission%20--%20dislodge%20Trump%20from%20the%20White%20House%2C%20then%20bow%20out%2C%20with%20elegance%2C%20after%20one%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20now%2081%2C%20will%20indeed%20be%20a%20one-term%20president%2C%20but%20under%20tumultuous%2C%20agonizing%20circumstances%3A%20long-simmering%20worries%20about%20his%20age%20and%20mental%20sharpness%20have%20exploded%20to%20doom%20him%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20second%20term%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20Biden%20said%20he%20was%20dropping%20his%20bid%20to%20run%20against%20Trump%20again%20in%20November%2C%20yielding%20to%20intense%20and%20growing%20pressure%20as%20polls%20showed%20most%20people%20even%20in%20his%20own%20Democratic%20Party%20felt%20he%20was%20too%20old%20to%20run%20for%20another%20term%2C%20much%20less%20serve%20four%20more%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefiance%20to%20dropping%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresidents%20tend%20to%20see%20their%20party%20take%20a%20beating%20in%20congressional%20elections%20held%20half%20way%20through%20their%20term%2C%20but%20Biden%20and%20his%20Democrats%20did%20surprisingly%20well%20in%202022.%20A%20feared%20hemorraghing%20of%20Democratic%20seats%20failed%20to%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20due%20in%20part%20to%20Americans'%20anger%20over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20ending%20of%20the%2050-year-old%20federal%20right%20to%20abortion%20--%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20court%20with%20three%20new%20conservatives%20judges%20appointed%20by%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergized%20by%20that%20strong%20showing%2C%20months%20later%20Biden%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20seek%20a%20second%20term%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%2