a%20survey%20of%201%2C435%20borewells%20constructed%20in%20commercial%20premises.%20Soon%2C%20notices%20were%20issued%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20led%20to%20the%20sealing%20of%20150%20borewells%20and%20the%20disconnection%20of%20their%20power%20connections.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20received%20at%20least%20800%20applications%20for%20NOCs.%20After%20speaking%20with%20the%20applicants%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20they%20lacked%20sufficient%20space%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20provided%20an%20alternative%20option%20of%20constructing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F192106%2Fbengaluru-rainwater-harvesting-school-save-water-environment-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%20%3C%2Fa%3Estructures%20on%20public%20buildings.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20initiative%2C%201%2C000%20public%20buildings%2C%20including%20schools%2C%20inter%20colleges%2C%20district%20hospitals%2C%20and%20various%20department%20offices%2C%20were%20equipped%20with%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems.%20Currently%2C%20Himanshu%20reports%20that%2070%20percent%20of%20government%20buildings%20now%20have%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%20installed%20by%20private%20entities%20to%20fulfil%20their%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20multi-pronged%20approach%20to%20rejuvenate%20groundwater%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fvaranasi-1-1721270267.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22As%20many%20as%20393%20artificial%20ponds%20spread%20across%20one-acre%20plots%20have%20been%20constructed%20for%20water%20conservation.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.