2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Be%20wild%20and%20free!%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20your%20instincts%20and%20exploring%20everything%20that%20comes%20your%20way%20is%20how%20Tejas%20likes%20to%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20primarily%20use%20Google%20Maps%20for%20planning%20our%20routes.%20We%20choose%20a%20starting%20point%20and%20an%20endpoint%2C%20then%20look%20for%20significant%20landmarks%20or%20places%20of%20interest%20along%20the%20way.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20travelling%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20we%20included%20stops%20at%20significant%20sites%20like%20the%2023%20Temples%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%20of%20India%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Save%20cost%20by%20budgeting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBudgeting%20for%20long-distance%20bike%20trips%20involves%20major%20expenses%20like%20fuel%2C%20food%2C%20and%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFuel%20costs%20are%20fixed%2C%20but%20we%20save%20on%20food%20and%20accommodation.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20stayed%20in%20budget%20hotels%20for%20as%20low%20as%20%E2%82%B9400%2C%20though%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20always%20suitable%20when%20travelling%20with%20my%20partner.%20We%20prefer%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F145039%2Fnews-maharashtra-airbnb-village-life%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20booking%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20safer%20and%20sometimes%20cheaper%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22He%20has%20travelled%20over%2060%2C000%20km%20on%20his%20bike%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357111%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHe%20has%20travelled%20over%2060%2C000%20km%20on%20his%20bike%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20food%2C%20we%20avoid%20high-end%20restaurants%2C%20opting%20for%20local%20eateries%20instead.%20We%20also%20carry%20bread%20and%20peanut%20butter%20for%20breakfasts%20and%20sometimes%20cook%20in%20Airbnbs%20which%20helps%20save%20on%20food%20expenses.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20push%20yourself%2C%20enjoy%20the%20journey!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20for%20long%20hours%20can%20be%20taxing%20but%20according%20to%20Tejas%2C%20it%20becomes%20easy%20with%20every%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhysically%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20follow%20a%20strict%20fitness%20routine%20but%20occasionally%20hit%20the%20gym.%20Our%20bodies%20have%20adapted%20to%20long%20rides%2C%20making%20biking%20more%20comfortable%20than%20long%20car%20journeys.%20The%20connection%20with%20our%20bike%20has%20developed%20over%20time%2C%20making%20long-distance%20rides%20manageable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Three%20Magic%20Words%3A%C2%A0%20Plan%2C%20Plan%20%26amp%3B%20Plan!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20planning%20their%20first%20long-distance%20bike%20trip%2C%20thorough%20p