mbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20he%20was%20also%20introduced%20to%20the%20hydroponics%20method%20of%20cultivation.%20Talking%20about%20its%20advantages%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CHydroponics%20allows%20us%20to%20grow%20leafy%20greens%20locally%20in%20a%20temperature-controlled%20environment%20all%20year%20round.%20It%20gives%20you%20more%20control%20over%20the%20growing%20part.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20how%20this%20method%20also%20saves%2090%20percent%20water%20compared%20to%20open-field%20farming%20as%20it%20keeps%20circulating%20it%20within%20the%20setup.%20This%20makes%20the%20whole%20technique%20a%20sustainable%20way%20of%20growing%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20reduces%20nutrient%20costs%2C%20as%20we%20only%20add%20the%20precise%20amount%20needed%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%20unlike%20in%20open-field%20farming%20where%20large%20quantities%20of%20fertilisers%20are%20used%20without%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20says%20that%20he%20invested%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20whole%20system%20on%20a%202.5%20acre%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20is%20only%20a%20one-time%20investment%2C%20yielding%20recurring%20benefits%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20he%20grows%20leafy%20greens%20hydroponically%20and%20harvests%20up%20to%20800%20kg%20of%20produce%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20leafy%20greens%2C%20the%20yield%20is%20almost%20five%20times%20greater%20compared%20to%20traditional%20land-based%20farming.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20beauty%20of%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20also%20grows%20bell%20peppers%20and%20seedless%20cucumbers%20in%20a%20naturally-ventilated%20polyhouse%20spanning%20across%201.5%20acres.%20Annually%2C%20he%20harvests%20up%20to%2090%20tonnes%20of%20seedless%20cucumbers%20and%20up%20to%2030%20tonnes%20of%20bell%20peppers.%20%E2%80%9CI%20get%20a%2030%20pe