eful%20for%20crops%20like%20lettuce%2C%20where%20the%20growth%20cycle%20reduces%20from%2090%20to%2040%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFormal%20training%20becomes%20essential%20in%20hydroponics%20to%20get%20maximum%20yield%20and%20return%20on%20investment.%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20maintain%20water%20temperature%20and%20control%20humidity%20levels.%20It%20is%20also%20essential%20to%20check%20for%20fungus%20attacks%20as%20they%20can%20quickly%20spread%20throughout%20the%20farm%20due%20to%20the%20shared%20water%20source.%20Using%20chillers%20can%20reduce%20temperatures%20to%2020%20degrees%20and%20minimise%20fungal%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20aspires%20to%20encourage%20more%20people%20to%20adopt%20hydroponics%20not%20just%20as%20an%20alternative%20cultivation%20technique%20but%20as%20a%20profitable%20and%20sustainable%20business%20venture%20as%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20meet%20the%20rising%20food%20demands%20in%20cities%20and%20address%20decreasing%20agricultural%20lands%20while%20supplementing%20higher%20incomes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20method%2C%20we%20can%20achieve%20higher%20yields%20in%20smaller%20areas%20and%20also%20boost%20our%20incomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20success%2C%20Pritpal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20heard%20about%20the%20children%20of%20doctors%20and%20lawyers%20following%20the%20same%20professions%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20that%20that%20mindset%20is%20lacking%20in%20farming.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20this%20thought%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20services%20are%20to%20remain%20the%20bedrock%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20economy%2C%20we%20need%20to%20make%20them%20more%20profitable.%20Working%20in%20this%20space%20and%20becoming%20a%20successful%20farmer%20has%20been%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20Personally%2C%20this%20entire%20experience%20has%20also%20made%20me%20more%20persistent%20and%20disciplined.%20Looking%20at%20my%20farm%20now%2C%20I%20feel%20content%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESource%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fijrpr.com%2Fuploads%2FV4ISSUE4%2FIJRPR11430.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20on%20hydroponics%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20By%20Shrestha%20Sanchaya%2C%20Ms%20Saritha%20S%20R%2C%20Mr%20Bhaskar%20A%2C%20Tesfaye%20Leul%2C%20Thapa%20Anushri%2C%20Agrawal%20Subham%2C%20Jaju%20Anish%20for%20International%20Journal%20of%20Research%20Publication%20and%20Reviews%2C%20published%20in%20April%2C%202023.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora.%20All%20photos%3A%20Pritpal%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721053991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-4-1721052314.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D356971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pritpal%20Singh%20turned%20to%20hydroponics%20to%20avoid%20soil-borne%20diseases.%20He%20runs%20a%20thriving%20business%20with%20thousands%20of%20leafy%20vegetables%20growing%20on%20his%202.5-acre%20land.%20He%20also%20started%20Farmcult%20to%20help%20other%20farmers%20switch%20to%20this%20innovative%20method.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356971%2Fhydroponics-farming-without-soil-sustainable-agriculture-farmer-increases-income-solar-energy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20%E2%80%98Entrepreneurial%20Households%E2%80%99%20Show%20How%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growth%20Story%20is%20Unfolding%20in%20Small%20Towns%20%26amp%3B%20Villages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Enmasse%20World.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Blind%20but%