serving%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahib%3C%2Fem%3E%20his%20much-awaited%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20calls%20this%20moment%20the%20one%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20was%20born!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FaJyz8f9XQSo%3Fsi%3DUfZb2ArDb5KspyWv%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovation%20at%20its%20best%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fleeting%20inclusion%20(of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20an%20ingenious%20one%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20it%20became%20a%20norm%20at%20Nizam%E2%80%99s.%20Raza%20was%20quick%20to%20note%20how%20the%20idea%20put%20a%20smile%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahib%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20face.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20decided%20to%20serve%20%E2%80%98that%20dish%E2%80%99%20to%20everyone%20who%20came%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20the%20restaurant.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20became%20a%20no-mess%20affair%20for%20anyone%20who%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrab%20a%20quick%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20ensured%20its%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20for%20the%20story%20of%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20hack%20of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20also%20decided%20to%20tweak%20its%20strategy%20a%20little.%20The%20iron%20skewers%20that%20were%20in%20use%20were%20proving%20heavy%20and%20tedious%2C%20and%20so%2C%20these%20were%20swapped%20with%20substitutes%20m