e%20not%20just%20mutton%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20vegetarian%20options%20and%20egg-layered%20meats%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20snack%20that%20was%20invented%20as%20a%20hasty%20binge-eat%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20became%20etched%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20memories%20for%20cultural%20reasons.%20As%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EMoney%20Control%3C%2Fem%3E%20underscores%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20roll%20during%20Durga%20Puja%2C%20it%20explores%20how%20amidst%20the%20slew%20of%20vendors%20selling%20fish%20fry%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekabiraji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fried%20fish%20fillets)%2C%20chilli%20chicken%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297834%2Fkolkata-phuchkawala-started-by-siblings-jyotirmoyee-debjyoti-saha-now-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephuchkas%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fried%20%3Cem%3Epuris%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20are%20filled%20with%20mashed%20potatoes%2C%20tamarind%20pulp%2C%20black%20chickpeas%20and%20flavoured%20with%20red%20chilli%2C%20cumin%20powder%2C%20black%20salt)%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20place%20selling%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%3C%2Fem%3E%20rolls%20with%20egg%20rolls%20being%20a%20crowd%20puller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20side%20of%20nostalgia%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Raj%20may%20have%20ended%20but%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20remained%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20minds%20and%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290130%2Forigin-of-samosa-sambhar-chaat-history-indian-food-recipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efond%20memories%20of%20the%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20television%20journalist%2C%20food%20critic%2C%20and%20author%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Indian%20Pantry%E2%80%99%20(2018)%2C%20Vir%20Sanghvi%20writes%20in%20a%20b